### Crown Jewel Rate (The Real Story)

Not all innovations are equal. Some are incremental. Others are structural — they reshape the platform, create new revenue models, or unlock entire categories of subsequent innovation. These are **Crown Jewels**: innovations flagged HIGH or CRITICAL for patent filing.

