TWELVE domain jumps in one session. The cross-domain surface is so wide that every conversation topic creates multiple innovation chains.

### The AI Amplification Effect

The compounding effect is further amplified by AI collaboration. The Founder-AI workflow (the "Chess Set") operates as follows:

1. **Founder provides the insight** — the creative spark, the real-world observation, the naming decision
2. **Bishop (Claude) provides the architecture** — connects the insight to existing innovations, identifies gaps, writes formal documentation
3. **Knight (Cursor) provides the implementation** — builds the code, deploys the pages, creates the database
4. **Pawn (Perplexity) provides the validation** — prior art searches, market comparisons, regulatory checks
5. **Rook (Gemini) provides the audit** — cross-references claims, verifies consistency

This workflow doesn't just ENABLE compounding innovation — it ACCELERATES the coupling constant k. The AI can hold the full innovation surface in context simultaneously, making cross-domain connections that a single human mind would miss.

**The Founder doesn't need to remember all 1,868 innovations.** The AI team does. When the Founder says "every business should offer subscriptions," the AI can immediately connect that to LB Card, Cold Start, Cost+20%, Multipliers, BandWagon, Local Sheet, Milk Routes, Cue Cards, and Earmarked Credits — all in seconds. The innovation surface isn't limited by human memory.

