5. Breakfast Runner → **Onboarding Credit** (labor economics / disintermediation)
6. Onboarding Credit → **Steward Path** (organizational design)

This chain — pet food → restaurant economics → delivery logistics → labor economics → organizational design → role architecture — crossed SIX domains in one session. Each jump was enabled by the existing foundation providing the connection point.

**Second chain in the same session:**
7. Storefronts → **HexIsle Ghost World mapping** (game design / spatial computing)
8. Ghost World → **Island Node Algorithm** (geographic computation)
