### 4.4 Cost Comparison

| Approach | Team Size | Monthly Cost | 5-Month Total | Output |
|----------|-----------|-------------|---------------|--------|
| Traditional startup | 20 engineers | $400K/mo | $2.0M | MVP |
| Outsourced dev shop | 10 engineers | $150K/mo | $750K | MVP |
